<h2 id="migration-considerations">🔄 Migration Considerations</h2>

Switching helpdesks mid-operation carries real risk. Our team has managed migrations in both directions, and here's what breaks:

<strong>From Zendesk to Gorgias:</strong> Historical tickets import cleanly, but custom fields and tags need mapping. Expect 2-4 weeks of parallel operation. The biggest pain point: retraining agents on a simpler interface that does things differently, not wrong—just differently.

<strong>From Gorgias to Zendesk:</strong> Ticket history imports, but you lose the rich order data sidebar until you configure Shopify apps. Budget 4-6 weeks for full feature parity. Teams accustomed to Gorgias' streamlined workflows initially feel Zendesk is slower.

Both platforms offer migration assistance on higher tiers. Use it.

